import React from 'react';
import {
    SidebarContainer,
    SidebarIcon,
    CloseIcon,
    SidebarContent,
    SidebarMenu,
    SidebarLink
}from './SidebarElements';

const Sidebar = () => {
    return (
        <>
            <SidebarContainer>
                <SidebarIcon>
                    <CloseIcon/>
                </SidebarIcon>
                <SidebarContent>
                    <SidebarMenu>
                        <SidebarLink>Inicio</SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink>Quienes Somos</SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink>Nuestros Proyectos</SidebarLink>
                        <SidebarLink>Contacto</SidebarLink>

                    </SidebarMenu>
                </SidebarContent>
            </SidebarContainer>
        </>
    )
}

export default SideBar
